# Redirect rules for Render static site
# See https://docs.render.com/redirects-rewrites

# Redirect non-www to www (canonical domain)
https://whyknot.live/* https://www.whyknot.live/:splat 301!
http://whyknot.live/* https://www.whyknot.live/:splat 301!
http://www.whyknot.live/* https://www.whyknot.live/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback - serve index.html for all non-file routes
/*    /index.html   200
